column2: SELECT za.SpecObjID, za.z, zi.e_bv_sfd FROM SpecObjAll AS za    JOIN galSpecInfo AS zi ON (za.SpecObjID = zi.SpecObjID)    JOIN PhotoObjAll AS po ON (po.objID = za.bestObjID)      JOIN Photoz AS zp ON (zp.objID = za.bestObjID)  WHERE    za.z > # AND za.zWarning = #    AND za.targetType = &&& AND za.survey = &&&    AND za.class = &&& AND zi.primtarget >= #    AND po.clean = # AND po.insideMask = #    AND (po.petroMag_r - po.extinction_r) <= #
